{
  "stem": "25591.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I was-- the-- the person who sort of organized this house, they gave me the task of getting medications for all the people who needed medications.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the reason I could do that was because I-- I had a sort of a-- not a military uniform, sort of a-- and not a Boy Scout uniform.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They-- they called it the [? levente ?] uniform.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Levente ?] was a-- a Hungarian historic term.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It's sort of a cadet, a-- a military cadet uniform with a Hungarian motifs and very handsome cap.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I move around the city.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And nobody bothered me, although I knew full well, because only Jews were circumcised, that if there was any suspicion and I had to drop my pants, that would be the end.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They-- they never asked me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I think that's why I survived, because I moved around the city throughout the worst period, both the Horthy period and the Szalasi period, to the very, very bitter end.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I did so, in retrospect, I'm convinced, not because of superior courage, but because of my conviction that I will not survive.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I might as well be of some help, of some use.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't want to exaggerate the importance of the things I did.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I-- I was carrying messages to Buda, to Pest, to-- to various people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was-- I was basically collecting medicine, collecting food.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Taking messages to various people was a very important function.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I did not engage in any military activity.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I-- I-- but I was-- I suspect it's probably fair to say I was part of the anti-Nazi underground, as a 16-year-old boy, weakening their efforts and strengthening the resistance.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
